# Frontend Application — AtlasOS Agent Rules

- Use TypeScript strict mode. No `any` types in new code.
- All components must be accessible (WCAG 2.1 AA): proper ARIA labels, keyboard navigation, color contrast.
- Bundle size budgets: initial load < 200KB gzipped.
- All user inputs must be sanitized before rendering.
- API calls must go through a centralized client with auth token injection.
- Visual regression tests required for shared components.
